### 1) Register Owner
POST https://localhost:5001/auth/register-owner
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email":"owner@example.com", "password":"DemoPass!123", "boatName":"My Boat" }

### 2) Login (istenirse)
POST https://localhost:5001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email":"owner@example.com", "password":"DemoPass!123" }

### 2.1) Token değişkeni
@token = {{login.response.body.$.token}}

### 3) Boat & Channels
GET https://localhost:5001/boats/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

POST https://localhost:5001/boats/channels
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name":"Güverte Işığı", "type":0, "pin":16 }

GET https://localhost:5001/boats/channels
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) Device create (X-New-Device-Key header’ını kopyala)
POST https://localhost:5001/devices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name":"ESP32-Bridge" }

### 5) Rotate key (opsiyonel)
POST https://localhost:5001/devices/{{create_device.response.body.$.id}}/rotate-key
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6) Toggle channel (komut kuyruğu + MQTT publish)
POST https://localhost:5001/channels/{{create_channel.response.body.$.id}}/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "state": true }

### 7) Telemetry query (grafik için)
POST https://localhost:5001/telemetry/query
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "fromUtc":"2025-10-01T00:00:00Z", "toUtc":"2099-01-01T00:00:00Z", "keys":["battery.voltage"], "page":1, "pageSize":50 }
